dc_description_s: New Hampshire. Geological and Mineralogical Survey 1868-1878. Companion text: The geology of New Hampshire. A report comprising the results of explorations ordered by the legislature / C.H. Hitchcock , J.H. Huntington. Concord: New Hampshire. Geological and Mineralogical Survey. 1868-1878. 5 pts. in 3 volumes:. v. 1. (pt. 1) Physical geography.--v. 2. (pt. 2) Stratigraphical geology.--v. 3. (pt. 3-5) Surface geology. Mineralogy and lithology. Economic geology. . Map of New Hampshire, 1816 by Philip Carrigain. Geologic map on six sheets. Topographic and glacial map on six sheets, missing one sheet. Plates: Camera profiles, Panoramic views. Julius Bien, New York [Lithographer].
dc_title_s: Atlas accompanying the report on the geology of New Hampshire. Sheet 13.
